dct_description_sm: Bird's-eye view of Bantam, Indonesia; relief shown pictorially. in upper left-hand margin: No. 6. Indexed for points of interest. Plate no. 6 from: Oud en nieuw Oost-Indien / François Valentyn. Dordrecht : Joannes van Braam ... [et al.], 1724-1726. Frederik Ottens engraved the plates and maps for F. Valentijn's Oud en nieuw Oost- Indien. cf. Tooley's dictionary of mapmakers, vol. 3, p. 362.
dct_publisher_sm: [Dordrecht ; Amsterdam : Joannes van Braam, Gerard onder de Linden, 1726]
